  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/c7930437deaeade35efcd6b36a23ae8b.poster.avif?t=1770332510\" width=730 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/c7930437deaeade35efcd6b36a23ae8b.webm?t=1770332510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/c7930437deaeade35efcd6b36a23ae8b.mp4?t=1770332510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Prepare to unravel the mysteries of The Anomaly Project!</strong>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CAN YOU AND YOUR TEAM FIGURE OUT WHATS OUT OF THE ORDINARY?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/b1c298a1b815977acadd9545c6c03409.poster.avif?t=1770332510\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/b1c298a1b815977acadd9545c6c03409.webm?t=1770332510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/b1c298a1b815977acadd9545c6c03409.mp4?t=1770332510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/cf0a1b1d14708d530c88a6626b86f147.avif?t=1770332510\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras_big/cf0a1b1d14708d530c88a6626b86f147.avif?t=1770332510 width=800 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SMii7Y</strong> <strong>•</strong> <strong>VanossGaming • KYRSP33DY • Forsen</strong> • <strong>Yogscast</strong> • H2ODelirious • Terroriser • Nogla • BasicallyIDoWork • Lui Calibe • 8-BitRyan • CaRtOoNz • TheDeluxe4 •  Elraenn • SideArms4Reason • ChilledChaosGAME • Hat Films • Kilira Cooper • Nino MssClick • luthfi halimawan • Jeni Gaming • <strong>And many more...</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/c8f49e09a52028e9aa645db0c04766e5.avif?t=1770332510\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras_big/c8f49e09a52028e9aa645db0c04766e5.avif?t=1770332510 width=800 height=52 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In The Anomaly Project you and <strong>co-players</strong> have to <strong>try and escape</strong> by noticing <strong>Anomalies</strong> and making the decision to go in either the Red tube or the Green tube. If you have decided correctly you progress to the next level. Otherwise you are reset to the first level. Will you ever escape...? </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/2e0d0c5169ef06843d0f6afa8b2993e4.avif?t=1770332510\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras_big/2e0d0c5169ef06843d0f6afa8b2993e4.avif?t=1770332510 width=800 height=50 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>1-8 player online co-op</strong><br>Explore a multiplayer experience with up to 8 players. Communicate and help each other through <strong>text chat</strong> or <strong>proximity voice chat</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Get to the exit</strong> <br>Navigating through the levels, some more mysterious than others, you'll encounter anomalies that defy logic and reason. Keep your senses sharp as you search for hidden clues and spot anomalies to get closer towards escaping at Level 10</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/34ebbe11cb5bdb8f03a3e4fb7f61d2cb.avif?t=1770332510\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras_big/34ebbe11cb5bdb8f03a3e4fb7f61d2cb.avif?t=1770332510 width=800 height=50 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 1-8 player online co-op</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Replayability</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Socialize with friends or strangers</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Chat & Voicechat</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Immerse yourself in a liminal space atmospheres</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Puzzles</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Get frightened, jumpscares</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Finding anomalies</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 5 Anomaly maps </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PLINKO!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE MULTIPLE MAPS, WITH EACH THEIR OWN THEMES AND CHALLENGING ANOMALIES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/3e33165588c2a6a006528c4b585e06f8.poster.avif?t=1770332510\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/3e33165588c2a6a006528c4b585e06f8.webm?t=1770332510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/3e33165588c2a6a006528c4b585e06f8.mp4?t=1770332510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SOME ANOMALIES ARE CRAZIER THAN OTHERS... OH YEAH, BE CAREFULL OF JUMPSCARES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/30fbf8fdb48ae37b1d07b1fabf0c32f7.poster.avif?t=1770332510\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/30fbf8fdb48ae37b1d07b1fabf0c32f7.webm?t=1770332510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/30fbf8fdb48ae37b1d07b1fabf0c32f7.mp4?t=1770332510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MAKE THE CORRECT CHOICES BY GOING EITHER IN THE RED OR GREEN PIPE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/2ca02a348d7a872cee0d2d1ec71b05e8.poster.avif?t=1770332510\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/2ca02a348d7a872cee0d2d1ec71b05e8.webm?t=1770332510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/2ca02a348d7a872cee0d2d1ec71b05e8.mp4?t=1770332510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPERIENCE THE CRAZINESS OF OUR NEW MAP 'STAIRS'</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/6def81a772b324e5cd9bc475882382be.poster.avif?t=1770332510\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"http