  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/c7930437deaeade35efcd6b36a23ae8b.poster.avif?t=1770332510\" width=730 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/c7930437deaeade35efcd6b36a23ae8b.webm?t=1770332510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/c7930437deaeade35efcd6b36a23ae8b.mp4?t=1770332510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Prepare to unravel the mysteries of The Anomaly Project!</strong>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CAN YOU AND YOUR TEAM FIGURE OUT WHATS OUT OF THE ORDINARY?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/b1c298a1b815977acadd9545c6c03409.poster.avif?t=1770332510\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/b1c298a1b815977acadd9545c6c03409.webm?t=1770332510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/b1c298a1b815977acadd9545c6c03409.mp4?t=1770332510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/cf0a1b1d14708d530c88a6626b86f147.avif?t=1770332510\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras_big/cf0a1b1d14708d530c88a6626b86f147.avif?t=1770332510 width=800 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SMii7Y</strong> <stro