ason. Keep your senses sharp as you search for hidden clues and spot anomalies to get closer towards escaping at Level 10</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/34ebbe11cb5bdb8f03a3e4fb7f61d2cb.avif?t=1770332510\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras_big/34ebbe11cb5bdb8f03a3e4fb7f61d2cb.avif?t=1770332510 width=800 height=50 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 1-8 player online co-op</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Replayability</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Socialize with friends or strangers</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Chat & Voicechat</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Immerse yourself in a liminal space atmospheres</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Puzzles</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Get frightened, jumpscares</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Finding anomalies</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 5 Anomaly maps </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PLINKO!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE MULTIPLE MAPS, WITH EACH THEIR OWN THEMES AND CHALLENGING ANOMALIES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/3e33165588c2a6a006528c4b585e06f8.poster.avif?t=1770332510\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/3e33165588c2a6a006528c4b585e06f8.webm?t=1770332510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/3e33165588c2a6a006528c4b585e06f8.mp4?t=1770332510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SOME ANOMALIES ARE CRAZIER THAN OTHERS... OH YEAH, BE CAREFULL OF JUMPSCARES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/30fbf8fdb48ae37b1d07b1fabf0c32f7.poster.avif?t=1770332510\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/30fbf8fdb48ae37b1d07b1fabf0c32f7.webm?t=1770332510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/30fbf8fdb48ae37b1d07b1fabf0c32f7.mp4?t=1770332510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MAKE THE CORRECT CHOICES BY GOING EITHER IN THE RED OR GREEN PIPE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/2ca02a348d7a872cee0d2d1ec71b05e8.poster.avif?t=1770332510\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/2ca02a348d7a872cee0d2d1ec71b05e8.webm?t=1770332510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/2ca02a348d7a872cee0d2d1ec71b05e8.mp4?t=1770332510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPERIENCE THE CRAZINESS OF OUR NEW MAP 'STAIRS'</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/6def81a772b324e5cd9bc475882382be.poster.avif?t=1770332510\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/6def81a772b324e5cd9bc475882382be.webm?t=1770332510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/6def81a772b324e5cd9bc475882382be.mp4?t=1770332510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GET A GOOD FRIGHT WITH YOUR FRIENDS, WITH THE NEW DARK MODE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/f2ff7e9a295f96abdff0dc4d0b466e1e.poster.avif?t=1770332510\" width=600 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/f2ff7e9a295f96abdff0dc4d0b466e1e.webm?t=1770332510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960770/extras/f2ff7e9a295f96abdff0dc4d0b466e1e.mp4?t=1770332510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare to unravel the mysteries of The Anomaly Project. Can you escape, or will you become lost forever? It's up to you, but remember, not everything is as it seems...</p>",
